{
  "events": [
    {
      "id": "action_network:fcccc6f3-924e-48fe-ad88-06779bb9d915",
      "name": "Dive-In to Fight for Healthcare",
      "date": "2026-07-25T14:00:00Z",
      "date_formatted": "2:00 PM, Saturday July 25, 2026",
      "month_year": "2026-07",
      "month_label": "July 2026",
      "status": "confirmed",
      "description": "<p><strong>July General Meeting of the </strong><strong>NYC DSA Healthcare Working Group</strong></p><p>Take the plunge to win universal healthcare!</p><p>We are holding an <strong>outdoor meeting</strong> followed by an optional dip in the New York City's largest pool in Astoria from 4pm.</p><p>We'll be near the War Memorial in a shady spot, between Astoria Pool and the East River.</p><p>Bring picnic blankets, folding chairs, water, sunscreen and anything else to be safe and comfortable on a hot day. We do not have a virtual option, but we will in August.</p><p><strong>Building on our electoral wins, can we re-orient our chapter to fight for the New York Health Act while millions of New Yorkers have their healthcare defunded by Trump? </strong></p><p>We have shared a <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1QjiEXuhoSYOBYhm8Letg5DoeDd_dGcKdom50zLwoJxM/edit?usp=sharing\">brief resolution</a> for our working group:</p><p><em>We resolve to build a movement to pass the New York Health Act in 2027 as a Citywide Priority Campaign, led by rank and file members of strategic unions.</em></p><p>Our organizing committee has heard overwhelmingly from our members that now is the time for NYHA - so we are holding this meeting to hear arguments for and against, and amendments to, this resolution that would channel our working group's efforts, enlisting talented and motivated people from across our organization and beyond to work towards this goal.</p><p>Read more about Citywide Priority Campaigns <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1HbMwJJcLtIsO3R30jlnGzVhAQ9viJELp6i2LV6L0YBY/edit?tab=t.0\">here</a></p><p>Read about how a Citywide Priority Campaign is adopted <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/15jqvMLnX_zX0k9Pdb8h_fpgZJM1zIQT2vUHsI0qDHXg/edit?tab=t.0\">here</a> (as we just saw with <a href=\"https://wecanbreakthechain.com/\">Break The Chain</a>)</p><p><br></p>",
      "browser_url": "https://actionnetwork.org/events/dive-in-to-fight-for-healthcare",
      "signup_url": "https://actionnetwork.org/events/dive-in-to-fight-for-healthcare",
      "location": "Shore Blvd, Astoria",
      "borough": "Queens"
    },
    {
      "id": "action_network:5d28fa00-2935-461d-93d6-a359f1b2b1f4",
      "name": "New York Health Act 101",
      "date": "2026-08-07T18:30:00Z",
      "date_formatted": "6:30 PM, Friday August 7, 2026",
      "month_year": "2026-08",
      "month_label": "August 2026",
      "status": "confirmed",
      "description": "<p>Come learn about the New York Health Act, a bill to de-privatize healthcare and send the extortionist insurance companies packing. No more premiums, deductibles, and co pays! No denials of care or medication and no restricted networks! There will be time Q&A and discussion.</p>",
      "browser_url": "https://actionnetwork.org/events/back-groundintro-to-new-york-health-act",
      "signup_url": "https://actionnetwork.org/events/back-groundintro-to-new-york-health-act",
      "location": "14 Jefferson St.",
      "borough": "New York"
    },
